<br>
It's important for everyone to understand stacking though, as their will be times that you need to switch sides to push the mob another way.<br>
<br>
Pushing definately does interrupt spells... a long time ago, I recall doing Vox... we had 2 chanters, one died almost instantly.  Having only one chanter left usually means death with Vox, but we were able to stack and push her around enough to prevent CHs.  Ended up taking her down with 21 because of the good pushing. <p><center>
